There's a Ji demon!

102
00:07:13,430 --> 00:07:14,290
Your Highness.

103
00:07:15,020 --> 00:07:15,880
Your Highness!

104
00:07:17,200 --> 00:07:18,030
What happened?

105
00:07:18,030 --> 00:07:19,090
