120
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:57,409
Yes.

121
00:08:01,500 --> 00:08:02,360
Your Highness!

122
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:04,110
Watch out, General!

123
00:08:04,110 --> 00:08:06,460
